title: Stellar Phoenix Repair for PDF v2.0.0.0
description:
Stellar Phoenix Repair for PDF v2.0.0.0

Stellar Phoenix Repair for PDF
Repairs Corrupt PDF Files of All Versions in Windows Systems
It is an effective Windows-based PDF repair software that can repair damaged PDF files. It restores forms, headers, footers, word art, clip art, page format, shapes, charts, and tables enclosed in the PDF files.
Repairs damaged or corrupt Adobe PDF files
Restores text data, graphs, watermark, and digital signatures from PDF files
Easily restores videos and music in corrupt PDF files
Repairs PDF files located on external storage devices
Supports 1.3, 1.4, 1.5, 1.6, and 1.7 versions of Adobe PDF files
Compatible with Windows 10, 8.1, 8, 7, Vista, and XP

This advanced PDF repair software can help you repair damaged PDF files irrespective of the severity of the corruption caused, without making any alterations in the structure of the PDF files.

Official Website: http://www.stellarinfo.com/file-repair/pdf-repair.php
